==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ainu
<hw>Ai"nu</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Said to be the native
name for man.]</ety> <def>One of a peculiar race found primarily in
Hokkaido, in the northern part of the empire of Japan, the Kurile
Islands, and nearby. They are believed to be the native inhabitants of
the Japanese islands. The Ainus are stout and short, with hairy bodies.
Also called <altname>Aino</altname> and <altname>hairy
Ainu</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ain't</ent>⟦br⟧
